pesticide.PPE: Long-sleeved shirt and long pants; Shoes plus socks

Safety_Information.general_Info: Harmful if swallowed. Wash thoroughly with soap and water after handling and before eating, drinking, chewing gum, tobacco or using the toilet.
Safety_Information.if_Swallowed: Call a poison control center or doctor immediately for treatment advice.
Safety_Information.physician_Note: Have the product or label with you when calling doctor, poison control or going for treatment.
